- mtk_memif_set_disable
- mtk_memif_set_addr
- mtk_memif_set_channel
- mtk_memif_set_rate
- mtk_memif_set_rate_substream
- mtk_memif_set_format
- mtk_memif_set_pbuf_size

2.extend mtk_base_memif_data struct for new platform

